  <div>
    <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Rules</h3>
    <ul class="mb-4 list-inside list-disc space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
      <li>We play on even weeks (week number 2, 4, 6, etc)</li>
      <li>We play best of 3 matches against four <strong>different</strong> opponents</li>
      <li>Use the same deck (including sideboard) for all matches</li>
      <li>Untimed rounds, but no "slow play", please</li>
      <li>We play Premodern*</li>
      <li>All proxies and gold border cards are allowed</li>
      <li>Optional, but encouraged, to send a decklist to the organizers</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mb-4 mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
