      <a href="https://premodernmagic.com/banned-watched#ban-list" class="{{ $linkClass }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Premodern banned list</a>
      here.
    </p>

    <hr class="mb-4 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700" />

